title: Cuban artist El Sexto is freed after 10 months in prison
text: > Entertainment Cuban artist El Sexto is freed after 10 months in prison Danilo Maldonado, better known as El Sexto, speaks on a mobile phone in the living room of his home after being released from jail, in Havana, Cuba, Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015. Maldonado was freed after 10 months behind bars for attempting to release two pigs painted with the names of Raul and Fidel Castro, the countryâ€™s current president and former leader. (AP Photo/Desmond Boylan)
